---
const { entry } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="features section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="features-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">WHEN YOU WANT THE BEST</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" {...entry?.edit.title}>Criminal Lawyer Springfield MO</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-title-wrap">
          <span class="feature-icon">+</span>
          <h3>COURTROOM<br/>FOCUSED</h3>
        </div>
        <p>That means our work is centered on trial practice. As trial lawyers, our attorneys’ work is heavily weighted toward complex criminal matters in Missouri state courts and federal courts. Our collaborative approach means you get the power of three instead of only one attorney.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-title-wrap">
          <span class="feature-icon">+</span>
          <h3>UNRIVALED<br/>EXPERIENCE</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Thomas Carver has litigated thousands of cases in the state and federal courts of Missouri. He has a reputation for success and gives 110% to every single client. Take advantage of this attorney’s experience whose sole focus is to employ it on your behalf.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-title-wrap">
          <span class="feature-icon">+</span>
          <h3>RECOGNIZED<br/>EXCELLENCE</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Thomas D. Carver highly regarded by legal peers for his trial expertise, exhaustive preparation, and integrity. This law firm was recognized as a 2017 U.S. News – Best Lawyers Best Law Firm and consistently receives individual awards for excellence in the courtroom.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { 
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background-color: #fff;
  }

  .features-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--color-lime);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature-title-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 0.8;
    color: var(--color-lime);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: -2px;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #888;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4rem; }
    .eyebrow { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .feature-title-wrap { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
